{"tid":159994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑評旺角三名年輕被告被判三年","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T11:46:22.000Z","uid":30807,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c151dd378563b9d7f4c6f18cda95c9523931b98","tid":159994,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂三名年輕被告，「暴動罪」罪名成立，同被判囚三年，包括一名港大學生。<br />\n<br />\n是否量刑過重？據「在雞蛋與石頭之間，我永遠偏袒支持雞蛋」的左派自由主義理論，持槍的七警代表強權的高牆，有計劃將示威者拉往暗角拳打腳踢，獲刑兩年，三名示威者向警方投擲玻璃瓶等物品，「明顯欲令警員受傷」－－請留意這個「欲」字－－卻判囚三年，是否過重，可以在中學通識課討論。<br />\n<br />\n但法官聲稱：「暴力就是暴力」，這句話的弦外之音，是同時也詮釋了七警判刑兩年的法理邏輯－－法官不考慮警察在現場如何經受壓力，不理會動機是執法清場還是愛國愛港，不理會有幾多人簽署抗議洋法官，「暴力就是暴力」，捐多少錢也不改變七警的暴力刑責性質，巧妙地為七警案定下結論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1418809081524944&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=272574169481780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1418809081524944%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D272574169481780&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=224fd347\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1418809081524944&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=272574169481780</a>"},{"pid":"b513c16b6f96a83aa01e69a7e03f2f8fab555fdc","tid":159994,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無成本，點解唔做？</span>"},{"pid":"637a82a3451d1558522baf3e2530d505bd2b7d1c","tid":159994,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b9f47d1cc9a4e89e604550521bd4d341f973c2","tid":159994,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab853157fb252e476709fd85e5140f5b1021e7b4","tid":159994,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT